'''子宫内膜样肿瘤'''（{{lang|en|Endometrioid tumors}}），是一类和[[子宫内膜癌|子宫内膜癌]]相似的肿瘤，其中三分之一的病例有鳞状上皮分化特征<ref name="urlDorlands Medical Dictionary:endometrioid tumor">{{cite web |url=http://www.mercksource.com/pp/us/cns/cns_hl_dorlands_split.jsp?pg=/ppdocs/us/common/dorlands/dorland/nine/13959057.htm |title=Dorlands Medical Dictionary:endometrioid tumor |work= |accessdate= }}{{Dead link|date=2018年7月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=no }}</ref>。

==卵巢==
发现于卵巢部位的子宫内膜样肿瘤属于[[卵巢肿瘤|卵巢肿瘤]]下的[[表面上皮间质肿瘤|表面上皮间质肿瘤]]，此类疾病在其总类的20%。原发性或边界性的变体非常罕见，绝大多数均为[[恶性肿瘤|恶性肿瘤]]。[[子宫内膜异位症|子宫内膜异位症]]与初级的[[子宫内膜癌|子宫内膜癌]]有关联。

在病理学的检查中，肿瘤通常呈囊性，有时为实性，一些会病变为囊性子宫内膜异位。在40%的案例中，会发现患者也患有子宫内膜样肿瘤<ref>{{cite book |editor1-last=Robbins |editor2-last=Cotran |title=Pathologic Basis of Disease |location=Philadelphia |publisher=Saunders |edition=7th |isbn=0-7216-0187-1 |year=2005 }}</ref>。

==子宫内膜==
此疾病也经常发现于子宫内膜中<ref name="pmid18156975">{{cite journal |author=Mulvany NJ, Allen DG |title=Combined large cell neuroendocrine and endometrioid carcinoma of the endometrium |journal=Int. J. Gynecol. Pathol. |volume=27 |issue=1 |pages=49–57 |pmid=18156975 |doi=10.1097/pgp.0b013e31806219c5 |url=http://meta.wkhealth.com/pt/pt-core/template-journal/lwwgateway/media/landingpage.htm?issn=0277-1691&volume=27&issue=1&spage=49 |date=January 2008 |access-date=2013-10-30 |archive-date=2012-05-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120525051358/http://meta.wkhealth.com/pt/pt-core/template-journal/lwwgateway/media/landingpage.htm?issn=0277-1691&volume=27&issue=1&spage=49 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{MeshName|Carcinoma,+Endometrioid}}</ref>。

第1级和第2级被视为“第一类”[[子宫内膜癌|子宫内膜癌]]，第3级被视为“第二类”<ref name="urlACS :: What Is Endometrial Cancer?">{{cite web |url=http://www.cancer.org/docroot/cri/content/cri_2_4_1x_what_is_endometrial_cancer.asp |title=ACS :: What Is Endometrial Cancer? |format= |work= |accessdate=2010-03-24 |archive-date=2010-06-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100620010337/http://www.cancer.org/docroot/cri/content/cri_2_4_1x_what_is_endometrial_cancer.asp |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

